verbose_text: To test whether mating inhibition is specific for Pry3 or whether this could also be observed upon overexpression of Pry1 or Pry2, MATa cells were transformed with plasmids overexpressing these Pry proteins, cells were mated to MATalpha cells for 5 h at 30degreesC and the number of zygotes formed during this period of time was quantified.
